{"tid":1069261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[女拳自主]偷食兼暴打老公　奧運金牌陳詩欣罪成！","createTime":"2019-03-20T00:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T01:15:15.000Z","uid":90515,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2535d94ff0ca2e3ffbf6ef33f2f11a379ddd8ac9","tid":1069261,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:08:42.000Z","msg":"中華台北跆拳奧運金牌女選手陳詩欣，雖然已經結婚並育有兩名子女，但竟偷食已婚教練，期間仲家暴老公，堅係離晒大譜。老公董俊男忍無可忍，上年將老婆同偷食男告上法庭，當地法院剛有判決，陳詩欣須向老公賠償30萬台幣。 <br />\n<br />\n1978年出世嘅陳詩欣，細細個就接受爸爸嘅跆拳道訓練，最終佢於2004年雅典奧運成功奪金，成為台灣之光。佢退役後同小學體育老師董俊男結婚定居花蓮，並開設道館推廣跆拳道。結婚後生咗兩名子女，以為陳詩欣會過住平凡但幸福嘅生活，但佢竟然同已婚跆拳教練陳正浩搭上，17年底2人被拍到兩周內兩次到酒店開房，仲喺街上旁若無人咁拍拖，完全忘記雙方各自已有家庭。 <br />\n<br />\n本身偷情已經唔啱，陳詩欣老公董俊男舊年仲大爆被家暴，話陳詩欣近半年來日夜都對佢「言語施暴」，仲試過喺個女面前郁手打自己，之後陳仲試過「踢開房門出腳攻擊」老公，董俊男直言係「接近發瘋的家庭暴力，自己已經無法再容忍這種狀況」。陳詩欣除打老公外，更迫女兒向佢匯報爸爸嘅一舉一動，如果做唔到就一巴巴打埋去，董俊男直斥老婆已冇晒人性同母愛。 <br />\n<br />\n舊年董俊男就將陳詩欣同陳正浩告上法庭，要求賠償100萬台幣，最終法院亦判董俊男勝訴，陳詩欣須賠償30萬台幣。二人到依家仲未離婚，但件事已搞到咁，睇嚟已返唔到轉頭。記者走訪走出法院後嘅陳詩欣，佢只係「謝謝大家的關心」，之後就悄然離去。 <br />\n<br />\nBy東網"},{"pid":"5257709ccbadd35d44393fd73739a1365883e251","tid":1069261,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:18:13.000Z","msg":"原來跆拳道有咁功用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用黎家暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8164ba59acb345fc4138fd5a2a0974a07bd311f0","tid":1069261,"uid":40867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:18:26.000Z","msg":"家暴偷食先30萬台幣...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a61ee915854a5fd5da392ca41253a206015806c","tid":1069261,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:18:47.000Z","msg":"早年台灣之光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15afe68eb725b90722c87a108f986feffe147a9e","tid":1069261,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVJQ8BB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVJQ8BB.png&h=dbe688b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"962f2dc12c3e32daf4fdb847abf3f6c0d71d58ea","tid":1069261,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"記得陳詩欣有段時間，去左做檳榔西施。"},{"pid":"65ea842d00b43fc8a3c0270f07947e57b5d182a5","tid":1069261,"uid":19066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:31:48.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79a31c8f14dcdf0608b36d95ed9791511a42dc3","tid":1069261,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:32:42.000Z","msg":"佢老公叫俊男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7cc7d85ddfc42a89c2afae56ddc46f4ae8eb97","tid":1069261,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:35:35.000Z","msg":"男性要好好保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532a02742fc3eff541716d906b1e5d4e421e6c5c","tid":1069261,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"女權講兩句"},{"pid":"b13c7cbe072af79004a0d95ddfe69ba5bb40bae0","tid":1069261,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79a31c8f14dcdf0608b36d95ed9791511a42dc3","tid":1069261,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T00:32:42.000Z","msg":"佢老公叫俊男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:04:39.000Z","msg":"佢細個既校園生活一定相當愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03845e94365d92b4ea34cc5f4e813d046feacb3e","tid":1069261,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1